Hello this is 911 I need help there.
Been an accident, a car crashed into a pole and the driver looks unconscious. I'm not sure if they're breathing. I checked and I don't think they are. There might be someone else in the car but I can't see clearly. I'm in a safe location but I don't know what to do. Please send help quickly.
So you can get this summer.
